item.title: Lavender
item.dc:creator: buithanhquynhnhu
item.description: It is an excellent insect repellent. The relaxing scent helps to promote a deep night's sleep. Scent also helps you relax when you're anxious. You don't need to burn essential oils by your bed to sleep well, just a pot of lavender by your window. It loves sunlight so place it in a sunny spot. In the fall and winter, the sun is not enough, so collect the seeds of the withered plants and plant it again in the spring.

item.title: Jasmine
item.dc:creator: buithanhquynhnhu
item.description: Jasmine blooms from 6-8 pm, when the temperature is low. Its fragrance is quite pleasant. Jasmine tea is very good for health. You just need a few flower branches to put in a tea cup and pour boiling water in, wait 10 minutes to have a great drink. Even when not served for jasmine tea, it acts as a room freshener and air purifier.
